{"tid":152526,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真學術討論】犯左罪第一時間做咩好？","createTime":"2017-03-11T19:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T06:43:57.000Z","uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be8a3814e8fccb029926a72bd6f46511b4f8b973","tid":152526,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T19:30:51.000Z","msg":"當我係前排扑爛金鋪偷戒指條友，呢個時候應該做咩做好？<br />\n我覺得呢種實拉到只係時間問題嘅案件應該即刻著草，聽講台灣（仲有澳門）同香港無條約會轉移罪犯，走佬去應該唔會比人捉到，好似之前單石屎藏屍D MK疑犯就走左去台灣宜家仲未捉返。咁睇落第一時間去台灣好似係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁，話哂兩地咁近，D消息好易傳過去，去到生唔生活到又係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有樣野叫國際刑警，唔知會唔會做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎各種情境代入，你地覺得第一時間做咩好？<br />\n利申：拎唔起錘仔"},{"pid":"867d461cf8474af08d06d665fe6459433c8a28e6","tid":152526,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T19:31:41.000Z","msg":"屌應該開起學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc27de200c1d4e288a5ed0070463be4c4062453","tid":152526,"uid":31522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T19:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd7127a032caeb6661610eb21a055b474b493db7","tid":152526,"uid":20671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T19:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/033344_851aa532fd94d901d315e468c0fa8627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F033344_851aa532fd94d901d315e468c0fa8627.jpg&h=26039b39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8322f91cf909399c77e2daf654b31ca438fa43a","tid":152526,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T19:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉左啦果班mk</blockquote><br />\n好似係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji